commit.message: Fixed README. Fixed license to LGPL 2.1.

Merge pull request #6 from sgayou/master

Security issues.

Attempted to fix an off-by-one error.

(*vtables) allocates num entries (0-num-1) and writes to num
to null terminate it.

Fix some common segfaults/crashes.

Better checking to prevent segfaults / strcpy on null / divide by
zero / unsigned & signed conversion errors.
Carefully free memory. Do not call dlclose before exit to avoid a crash.

Merge pull request #4 from floppym/master

Improve Makefile
Fixed demangling of typeinfos and pure virtual functions.
